FBIS4-4147 "drchi083_a_94017" FBIS-CHI-94-083 Daily Report 28 Apr 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS General `Foreign Experts' Gather Together in Beijing for May Day `Foreign Experts' Gather Together in Beijing for May Day OW2804165094 Beijing XINHUA in English 1425 GMT 28 Apr 94 OW2804165094 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, April 28 (XINHUA) -- More than 600 foreign experts working in China and their Chinese colleagues gathered together here at a evening party to celebrate the International Labor Day which falls on May 1. The evening party was sponsored by China's State Bureau of Foreign Experts Affairs.
